quote><br />\n<br />\n嘩佢咁仆街架<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c77a4706d9ca1b9789fc9b1df6d44222df49383","tid":46653,"uid":30862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T07:51:21.000Z","msg":"高質回帶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"929cb8639f583d1493ddb4bdac150550404e4a4a","tid":46653,"uid":22949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T07:55:53.000Z","msg":"update到iphone7同VR<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e31286226fefc5c1417f21c7bace3bb03ae74f8b","tid":46653,"uid":20592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T07:58:45.000Z","msg":"又loop ar<br />\n次次都睇到喊出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83a4fa3a22b41899d717e444ba5697a3e2ef1995","tid":46653,"uid":49428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T08:00:18.000Z","msg":"潮文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f78a8c289c6fc4e8bc89f25d708deecf76c8610","tid":46653,"uid":8528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T08:00:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>死傻仔！擺明比人昆左啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n難分真與假<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"529141764c84894324e75ad927ffe3ee96afa4a7","tid":46653,"uid":16889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T08:10:05.000Z","msg":"其實最柒係每次都有人爆響口話潮文潮文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁樣我點樣block d新會員<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" c